2
00:00:47,000 --> 00:00:49,240
The person I'm going to serve as my lord

3
00:00:49,240 --> 00:00:53,220
is linked to him by blood, that Pok Doo that's hard to control.

4
00:00:53,220 --> 00:00:56,330
According to military strategies,

5
00:00:57,160 --> 00:01:04,630
if you want the commander to collapse, then aim for his horse first.

6
00:01:04,630 --> 00:01:09,960
Teacher Sam Bong, my place in that cave,

7
00:01:09,960 --> 00:01:15,670
please take care of it well. I will surely come back to it.

8
00:01:15,670 --> 00:01:18,710
The An Byeon Chaek wasn't sent by Lee Seong Gye.

9
00:01:18,710 --> 00:01:22,250
His son, Lee Bang Won, stamped it with his father's seal and forged it.

10
00:01:22,250 --> 00:01:24,140
Lee Bang Won?

11
00:01:24,140 --> 00:01:27,500
So, things have become more difficult.

12
00:01:27,500 --> 00:01:30,670
Now, Lee In Gyeom will counterattack.

13
00:01:30,670 --> 00:01:35,300
Lee Bang Won, Lee Bang Won!

14
00:01:35,300 --> 00:01:37,640
Did you suddenly think of a good idea?

15
00:01:37,640 --> 00:01:44,600
Have you thought about the thing that is the hardest to understand in this whole palace?

16
00:01:50,060 --> 00:01:52,640
How is it that Lee Seong Gye's An Byeon Book

17
00:01:52,640 --> 00:01:56,500
was favored by Hong In Bang and Gil Tae M? It was this.

18
00:01:56,500 --> 00:01:59,500
You've pinpointed it.

19
00:01:59,500 --> 00:02:05,320
Now, I will make people understand that.

20
00:02:11,660 --> 00:02:13,270
What is that?

21
00:02:13,270 --> 00:02:14,780
I-It's nothing.

22
00:02:14,780 --> 00:02:19,740
Nothing? You're face suddenly went pale. What is it that you're being like that?

23
00:02:24,040 --> 00:02:26,860
Through the An Byeon Book, the tax revenue of the now secured Northeastern side

24
00:02:26,860 --> 00:02:29,910
will be divided between Hong In Bang, Gil Tae Mi, and Lee Seong Gye

25
00:02:29,910 --> 00:02:31,990
in a secret agreement?

26
00:02:43,060 --> 00:02:47,320
It's only an anonymous letter. There isn't any basis for it, either.

27
00:02:53,690 --> 00:02:57,550
No, no. It couldn't be.

28
00:02:57,550 --> 00:03:01,560
Lee Seong Gye is not that kind of person. Certainly.

29
00:03:07,310 --> 00:03:10,120
Pan Yi Bu Sa,
(Pan Yi Bu Sa: a government post name)

30
00:03:11,380 --> 00:03:15,520
I need to ask for a favor.

31
00:03:15,520 --> 00:03:19,170
Yes. Please speak.

32
00:03:25,490 --> 00:03:27,950
General!

33
00:03:32,160 --> 00:03:36,670
I... have something I want to consult with you about.

34
00:03:36,670 --> 00:03:38,650
What is it, Pan Yi Bu Sa?

35
00:03:38,650 --> 00:03:43,690
Have you heard about the stories going around now?

36
00:03:44,580 --> 00:03:49,430
Are you talking about the anonymous letter that nobody can confirm?
(Choi Yeong)

37
00:03:52,720 --> 00:03:56,420
You have to read this.

38
00:03:58,730 --> 00:04:06,150
I want to tell you that a series of letters like this shouldn't be overlooked.

39
00:04:06,150 --> 00:04:08,880
Isn't it strange?

40
00:04:08,880 --> 00:04:13,580
If the contents of that letter aren't true, then just why

41
00:04:13,580 --> 00:04:19,570
would you, Gil Tae Mi and Hong In Bang, vote in favor of the An Byeon Book when you have a really bad relationship with Lee Seong Gye?

42
00:04:19,570 --> 00:04:23,170
That's definitely because,after stabilizing the Northeastern side (Woo Hak Joo),

43
00:04:23,170 --> 00:04:26,230
there will be a strong defense.

44
00:04:27,700 --> 00:04:31,390
Ah, so that was it.

45
00:04:31,390 --> 00:04:35,540
For the stability of the Northeastern side?

46
00:04:37,730 --> 00:04:43,860
But during the last Do Dang meeting, what did you say?

47
00:04:43,860 --> 00:04:48,890
"Is Lee Seong Gye the only one protecting the country?" Didn't you say that?

48
00:04:48,890 --> 00:04:50,600
That is...

49
00:04:50,600 --> 00:04:53,550
Look here. Seung Rok Dae Bu!
(Seung Rok Dae Bu: a government official during the Goryeo era)

50
00:04:54,450 --> 00:04:59,450
Kwa Jeuk...Mul Tan Gae?
(Kwa Jeuk Mul Tan Gae: Not hesitating to immediately fix what you did wrong)
(Gil Tae Mi)

51
00:04:59,450 --> 00:05:02,050
There's a saying like this!

52
00:05:02,050 --> 00:05:05,670
According to Jung Yong! Jung Yong!
(Jung Yong: Doctrine of the Mean, one of the 4 Books of Confucian texts)

53
00:05:08,170 --> 00:05:10,160
Non Eo.
(Non Eo: Analects, one of the four books)

54
00:05:10,160 --> 00:05:13,450
Non Eo. According to Non Eo!

55
00:05:13,450 --> 00:05:18,290
It means that a superior person should not be afraid of fixing what he did wrong.

56
00:05:18,290 --> 00:05:23,800
But right now, I am showing you my image as a superior person.

57
00:05:23,800 --> 00:05:25,720
What is wrong with that?

58
00:05:25,720 --> 00:05:27,810
Ah, seriously.

59
00:05:30,500 --> 00:05:33,890
Did I really say that?

60
00:05:33,890 --> 00:05:38,770
Anyway, there was an uproar at the royal palace because of this so we need to investigate.

61
00:05:38,770 --> 00:05:42,890
Investigate? What investigation do you need?

62
00:05:43,610 --> 00:05:45,360
What?
(He spoke informally to someone older than him.)

63
00:05:46,270 --> 00:05:50,230
What? You bastard!

64
00:05:50,230 --> 00:05:53,240
-Bastard? Bastard?
-What, you bastard?

65
00:05:53,240 --> 00:05:56,190
- I ought to just--
- Bastard? Why?

66
00:05:56,190 --> 00:05:57,730
Hey, you bastard!

67
00:05:57,730 --> 00:05:59,810
Stop!

68
00:06:05,110 --> 00:06:07,630
Prime Minister.

69
00:06:07,630 --> 00:06:08,440
Me?

70
00:06:08,440 --> 00:06:12,970
A few days ago, your son got nominated as a Gam Chang Gwan in the Northeastern region.

71
00:06:12,970 --> 00:06:17,560
Gam Chang Gwan: an official rank given to someone who inspects tax and warehouses

72
00:06:17,560 --> 00:06:22,060
What are you saying? It's something that I didn't know.

73
00:06:27,050 --> 00:06:30,350
There's a written certification like this and you're still denying it?

74
00:06:30,350 --> 00:06:33,550
Go Gong Chong Rang Gil Yoo has been appointed as a Northeastern region tax and warehouse inspector.

75
00:06:33,550 --> 00:06:39,570
If it's the Gam Chang Gwan, then isn't that the one who inspects taxes in the Northeaster region?

76
00:06:39,570 --> 00:06:41,870
How could this be!

77
00:06:41,870 --> 00:06:44,510
Even with this, are you still going to say that you didn't have a secret agreement with Lee Seong Gye?

78
00:06:44,510 --> 00:06:46,080
Then, it is true...

79
00:06:46,080 --> 00:06:49,300
- It's true?
- How could this be?

80
00:06:49,300 --> 00:06:51,330
It's that position too.

81
00:06:52,650 --> 00:06:55,490
Okay, okay, okay.

82
00:06:56,530 --> 00:06:59,060
Although it is anonymous,

83
00:06:59,060 --> 00:07:04,650
since some of the Do Dang members have spoken up about their will,

84
00:07:05,620 --> 00:07:10,760
I'm thinking of going through with the investigation...
(Lee In Gyeom)

85
00:07:19,380 --> 00:07:21,240
My Lord!

86
00:07:21,240 --> 00:07:24,070
If Gil Yoo has really been appointed as a tax inspector,

87
00:07:24,070 --> 00:07:28,320
this series of circumstances is enough to be suspicious.

88
00:07:28,320 --> 00:07:32,580
Do you really think that General Lee Seong Gye is that kind of person...
(Po Eun: Jeong Mong Joo)

89
00:07:32,580 --> 00:07:35,890
No. Do you think he's someone who would do that?

90
00:07:35,890 --> 00:07:37,400
Lord.

91
00:07:37,400 --> 00:07:43,200
Didn't we already witness the unpleasant crumbling of heroes many times?

92
00:07:45,570 --> 00:07:48,520
It's just a groundless rumor.

93
00:07:53,130 --> 00:07:58,900
It's a rumor, just a rumor. But in that rumor, General Lee Seong Gye

94
00:07:58,900 --> 00:08:01,820
will get the most fatal blow.

95
00:08:01,820 --> 00:08:05,440
It is indeed fatal. Integrity...

96
00:08:05,440 --> 00:08:09,710
He is attacking Lee Seong Gye's biggest weapon, his integrity.

97
00:08:09,710 --> 00:08:13,550
Yes. As is expected of Lee In Gyeom.

98
00:08:13,550 --> 00:08:16,140
I need to go to Ham Joo. I need to meet General Lee Seong Gye.

99
00:08:16,140 --> 00:08:21,310
A report came in saying that Lee Shin Jeok is coming to Gaegyeong by Lee Seong Gye's order.

100
00:08:21,310 --> 00:08:26,110
Please decide after meeting him first. He'll be here soon.

101
00:08:28,120 --> 00:08:30,310
Just what are you saying?

102
00:08:30,310 --> 00:08:32,340
It's as you heard, Hyung-nim.

103
00:08:32,340 --> 00:08:37,440
So, at a time like this when the war with Ho Bal Do has started, you came here to Gaegyeong?
(Lee Bang Woo)

104
00:08:37,440 --> 00:08:43,210
Yes. I already relayed the message and was about to go back immediately, but you were scolding me.
(Lee Bang Gwa)

105
00:08:45,220 --> 00:08:52,130
Then immediately withdraw the An Byeon Book, give the documents to the Do Dang, and go back to Ham Joo.

106
00:08:52,130 --> 00:08:55,250
But Hyung-nim.

107
00:08:55,250 --> 00:08:57,760
Is withdrawing the An Byeon Book right, or...

108
00:08:57,760 --> 00:09:03,250
Whether it is right or wrong, Father has already decided. We can just follow him.

109
00:09:03,250 --> 00:09:06,710
He is our father but he is also the leader of the Ga Byeol Cho.
(Ga Byeol Cho: Lee Seong Gye's secret private army.)

110
00:09:06,710 --> 00:09:09,680
It's what we have to do according to our military discipline.

111
00:09:10,440 --> 00:09:15,630
How could you also be played by Bang Won's lies?

112
00:09:15,630 --> 00:09:20,460
Where are you going? Where are you going that you're packing you're stuff?

113
00:09:20,460 --> 00:09:21,480
Ham Joo.

114
00:09:21,480 --> 00:09:22,830
Ham Joo?

115
00:09:22,830 --> 00:09:24,750
To take responsibility.

116
00:09:25,520 --> 00:09:31,160
You said that being an adult is taking responsibility.
(Lee Bang Won)

117
00:09:32,510 --> 00:09:34,350
Withdrawing the An Byeon Book?

118
00:09:34,350 --> 00:09:39,330
Lee Bang Gwa has the documents to withdraw the An Byeon Book and he has arrived in Gaegyeong.

119
00:09:39,330 --> 00:09:41,740
Where is Lee Bang Won's house? Lead me there.

120
00:09:41,740 --> 00:09:43,410
What are you going to do?

121
00:09:43,410 --> 00:09:48,350
Gyo Ui Lee is going to Lee Bang Won's house, right? First, we have to stop him.

122
00:09:48,350 --> 00:09:53,290
In the end, there's a sequence to giving up. It has to be that way to allow the next move.

123
00:09:56,760 --> 00:10:02,810
Hey, I'm fine with you going wherever, but you have to tell me where ajussi is before you go.

124
00:10:02,810 --> 00:10:04,690
Young Master!

125
00:10:06,750 --> 00:10:07,850
Did you come from Ham Joo?

126
00:10:07,850 --> 00:10:11,010
Ah, there's a big problem. The general told me to catch you immediately.
(Jo Young Gyu)

127
00:10:11,010 --> 00:10:13,950
Like your legs will get clubbed... Like, really! Well, it's that kind of atmosphere.

128
00:10:13,950 --> 00:10:16,210
I'm already on my way to Ham Joo anyway.

129
00:10:16,210 --> 00:10:19,580
I'll go and settle things.

130
00:10:21,310 --> 00:10:27,550
Aigoo, I should've stopped him back then. What kind of hard work is this when the An Byeon Book will be withdrawn anyway...

131
00:10:27,550 --> 00:10:28,540
What did you say?

132
00:10:28,540 --> 00:10:30,500
Young Master Bang Gwa came with me.

133
00:10:30,500 --> 00:10:34,380
He has the documents to withdraw the An Byeon Book.

134
00:10:34,380 --> 00:10:36,230
You bastard!

135
00:10:38,680 --> 00:10:43,390
No matter how young and foolish you are, how could you behave in such an immature manner?

136
00:10:43,390 --> 00:10:47,550
Everything is my fault. Still, how could you withdraw the An Byeon Book?

137
00:10:47,550 --> 00:10:49,660
That will not do.

138
00:10:49,660 --> 00:10:53,000
I will go to Ham Joo and receive my punishment, whatever it is.

139
00:10:53,000 --> 00:10:55,890
You must not withdraw it, Hyung-nim!

140
00:10:57,160 --> 00:10:59,860
This bastard still cannot clear his head.

141
00:10:59,860 --> 00:11:02,100
There's an execution in this mountain-like work.

142
00:11:02,100 --> 00:11:06,350
Did you see the Ga Byeol Cho and Northeastern region that you rattled?

143
00:11:06,350 --> 00:11:10,450
Go to Ham Joo and accept your punishment. You will be on detention.

144
00:11:14,140 --> 00:11:17,880
Hurry and go to the Do Dang. Hand over the documents of withdrawal to them.

145
00:11:18,810 --> 00:11:20,480
Yes, Hyung-nim.

146
00:11:23,910 --> 00:11:27,310
Hyung-nim! You must not do this.

147
00:11:27,310 --> 00:11:31,690
Please hold on to it for just a bit. I will meet Father and I can persuade him.

148
00:11:31,690 --> 00:11:33,860
Please wait.

149
00:11:36,370 --> 00:11:38,760
Bang Won, you bastard!

150
00:11:53,470 --> 00:11:57,020
What are the police doing here?

151
00:11:57,020 --> 00:12:01,710
Is General Lee Seong Gye's fifth son, Lee Bang Won here?

152
00:12:05,310 --> 00:12:08,310
He is but why are you looking for him?

153
00:12:08,310 --> 00:12:13,670
He is being charged of having illegal dealings with Head of Seonggyungwan, Hong In Bang, to get the An Byeon Book approved.

154
00:12:13,670 --> 00:12:14,560
Arrest him!

155
00:12:14,560 --> 00:12:16,300
Yes!

156
00:12:22,150 --> 00:12:24,550
It is you, Hap Ha.

157
00:12:24,550 --> 00:12:27,840
In thinking of your next step regarding Head of Seonggyungwan, Hong In Bang,
(Cho Young: Hwa Sa Dan Owner)

158
00:12:27,840 --> 00:12:30,840
you must be busy.

159
00:12:31,600 --> 00:12:35,640
That's why you called on to your Jang Goon.
(Jang Goon: General, a chess piece)

160
00:12:35,640 --> 00:12:37,620
I...

161
00:12:38,380 --> 00:12:42,530
I didn't call my General for Hong In Bang.

162
00:12:43,860 --> 00:12:45,410
What?

163
00:12:46,030 --> 00:12:48,180
Then for whom?

164
00:12:48,180 --> 00:12:52,610
I think Hong In Bang is just being controlled.

165
00:12:52,610 --> 00:12:57,520
Then, is Lee Seong Gye standing behind Hong In Bang?

166
00:12:57,520 --> 00:12:59,900
No.

167
00:12:59,900 --> 00:13:05,860
A glimmering shadow behind Lee Seong Gye and Hong In Bang...

168
00:13:06,530 --> 00:13:11,920
I've sent the General to that shadow.

169
00:13:12,630 --> 00:13:16,590
Even if you meet with Gyo Ui Lee, how will you block the documents?

170
00:13:24,080 --> 00:13:26,340
Isn't that Bang Won?

171
00:13:29,660 --> 00:13:34,880
The shadow behind Lee Seong Gye.

172
00:13:40,090 --> 00:13:44,450
Can you see and receive it this time?

173
00:14:30,390 --> 00:14:32,810
We can gain four things from just this one happening.

174
00:14:32,810 --> 00:14:36,680
First, if the arrested Bang Won, in the middle of being tortured,

175
00:14:36,680 --> 00:14:38,650
has something bad happen to him,

176
00:14:38,650 --> 00:14:41,840
the forging of the An Byeon Book documents will be buried.

177
00:14:41,840 --> 00:14:43,410
What?

178
00:14:43,410 --> 00:14:46,510
Second, if that happens, Lee Seong Gye and Lee In Gyeom

179
00:14:46,510 --> 00:14:49,020
will have already crossed a river of no return.

180
00:14:49,020 --> 00:14:54,190
Lee Seong Gye will be standing in the position you wanted him in.

181
00:14:55,080 --> 00:14:58,510
Then, third. The thing you are worried about, Bon Won,

182
00:14:58,510 --> 00:15:01,390
that serious Pok Doo,

183
00:15:01,390 --> 00:15:03,780
will be naturally solved.

184
00:15:03,780 --> 00:15:08,070
So are you just going to watch over this situation?
(Lee Shin Jeok)

185
00:15:08,070 --> 00:15:13,050
Are you just going to let a person without sin be tortured to death?

186
00:15:15,360 --> 00:15:20,100
Sin and death have never been related to begin with.

187
00:15:20,100 --> 00:15:23,490
You don't die because you have sinned

188
00:15:23,490 --> 00:15:27,260
and you don't live because you have no sins.

189
00:15:27,260 --> 00:15:30,090
In this country, has any death

190
00:15:30,920 --> 00:15:33,810
been related to sin?

191
00:15:33,810 --> 00:15:38,130
What? This wench is wholeheartedly wishing ill upon others!

192
00:15:38,130 --> 00:15:41,740
We are all gathered to change that kind of country!

193
00:15:44,110 --> 00:15:47,210
Elder Bon Won, this must never happen.

194
00:15:47,210 --> 00:15:49,460
Let's say that Bang Won did something wrong.

195
00:15:49,460 --> 00:15:52,480
Even so, you can't sacrifice him to this kind of conspiracy.

196
00:15:54,230 --> 00:15:56,940
I only follow Elder Bon Won's will.

197
00:15:56,940 --> 00:16:00,140
I will follow your decision.

198
00:16:02,840 --> 00:16:06,490
Bug. A bug.

199
00:16:18,120 --> 00:16:22,310
A bug has finally started crawling in my mind.

200
00:16:22,310 --> 00:16:27,540
No, it was from the moment I saw Lee Bang Won arrested.

201
00:16:30,720 --> 00:16:32,990
What Yeon Hee said was right.

202
00:16:32,990 --> 00:16:35,990
If I let Lee Bang Won be tortured to death,

203
00:16:35,990 --> 00:16:41,000
the many things that came to be might get easily and swiftly be resolved.

204
00:16:42,890 --> 00:16:47,500
I can just turn my head away for a bit.

205
00:16:47,500 --> 00:16:49,430
In that smooth-sailing process,

206
00:16:49,430 --> 00:16:52,560
how many people need to die?

207
00:16:52,560 --> 00:16:55,530
That's a process we need to go through.

208
00:16:55,530 --> 00:16:59,220
Every great cause is followed by hardship.

209
00:16:59,220 --> 00:17:01,640
Taking responsibility.

210
00:17:01,640 --> 00:17:03,530
I've already prepared myself for that.

211
00:17:06,550 --> 00:17:10,090
It's a bug. A bug.
(Sam Bong: Jeong Do Jeon)

212
00:17:10,090 --> 00:17:11,650
But...

213
00:17:11,650 --> 00:17:13,460
We have to save Young Master Bang Won!

214
00:17:13,460 --> 00:17:15,920
We need to do something, whatever it is.

215
00:17:15,920 --> 00:17:20,220
Hurry and send the documents to cancel everything, okay?

216
00:17:23,760 --> 00:17:25,810
Give them to me.

217
00:17:25,810 --> 00:17:27,830
What are you going to do?

218
00:17:34,920 --> 00:17:38,170
I will not send this.

219
00:17:38,920 --> 00:17:41,610
- Hyung-nim!
- This is how Lee In Gyeom

220
00:17:41,610 --> 00:17:44,140
is proclaiming war against our family.

221
00:17:44,140 --> 00:17:48,300
The Ga Byeol Cho doesn't avoid war!

222
00:17:49,520 --> 00:17:50,370
Hyung-nim.

223
00:17:50,370 --> 00:17:53,690
You two command the Gaegyeong Ga Byeol Cho

224
00:17:53,690 --> 00:17:56,010
and be ready and in position.

225
00:17:56,010 --> 00:17:58,500
- Yes, Hyung-nim.
- Yes!

226
00:17:58,500 --> 00:18:01,750
I will go to Ham Joo, report the situation to Father,

227
00:18:01,750 --> 00:18:04,990
and receive a strict military command.

228
00:18:14,880 --> 00:18:20,120
He is being charged with illegal dealing with Head of Seonggyungwan Hong In Bang to get the An Byeon Book approved.

229
00:18:21,380 --> 00:18:23,280
Hong In Bang...

230
00:18:23,280 --> 00:18:24,730
You met?

231
00:18:24,730 --> 00:18:27,580
Yes. That night when I got attacked,

232
00:18:27,580 --> 00:18:31,270
it is true that Lee Bang Won came to me.
(Hong In Bang)

233
00:18:31,270 --> 00:18:34,450
We didn't have a secret agreement but there's also no evidence of that.

234
00:18:34,450 --> 00:18:36,620
What's the use of evidence?

235
00:18:36,620 --> 00:18:39,690
If Lee Bang Won confesses, then that would be the evidence.

236
00:18:39,690 --> 00:18:44,720
How can such a young kid endure police torture?

237
00:18:47,430 --> 00:18:49,320
Let's kill him.

238
00:18:50,310 --> 00:18:52,230
