499
00:38:06,150 --> 00:38:07,800
How?

500
00:38:07,800 --> 00:38:12,580
When I was young, I also came from the Western district.

501
00:38:13,400 --> 00:38:17,230
I hope that you don't say anything to Boon Yi.

502
00:38:17,230 --> 00:38:21,710
Also, please do not ask me about the story behind it.

503
00:38:23,310 --> 00:38:28,120
My brother left then and there was also no news regarding Unni Yeon Hee.

504
00:38:29,160 --> 00:38:33,650
Could that Yeon Hee have been you?

505
00:38:33,650 --> 00:38:38,710
Where in Goryeo can you find a person without a story? I will not ask you.

506
00:38:38,710 --> 00:38:40,250
Where is Boon Yi?

507
00:38:40,250 --> 00:38:44,800
At a time when the people are dying of hunger, there was a secret agreement regarding tax revenues!

508
00:38:44,800 --> 00:38:48,450
We will clearly expose what is true and what is not.

509
00:38:48,450 --> 00:38:50,060
We will clearly expose it!

510
00:38:50,060 --> 00:38:54,210
Even the students are like this, I

511
00:38:54,210 --> 00:38:57,430
cannot reject an investigation.

512
00:38:57,430 --> 00:39:03,400
But you already caught and tortured an innocent Lee Bang Won, so that should do. What else do you want? You can't even make him confess!

513
00:39:03,400 --> 00:39:08,390
If that young child is innocent to that extent, don't you think he would confess in that scary place?

514
00:39:08,390 --> 00:39:12,900
Yes. It's either that he can't trust his conviction

515
00:39:12,900 --> 00:39:16,020
or that he trusts Lee Seong Gye with everything.

516
00:39:17,140 --> 00:39:20,970
Is Lee Seong Gye someone who would accept an offer like that?

517
00:39:22,700 --> 00:39:27,030
I only voted in favor of the An Byeon Book because it will be a great help to Goryeo's defense.

518
00:39:27,030 --> 00:39:33,060
Of course, it's also because I wanted to be in a higher position than you in this political war.

519
00:39:33,060 --> 00:39:36,490
But there was no such thing as a secret agreement.

520
00:39:36,490 --> 00:39:40,980
That's why I am going to do an investigation.

521
00:39:40,980 --> 00:39:45,620
What's the use of saying whether there was a secret agreement or not here?

522
00:39:45,620 --> 00:39:50,390
But how can we trust that investigation?

523
00:39:51,750 --> 00:39:55,400
There's one person in the investigation office, like a Byek Chang Ho.
(Byeok Chang Ho: A stubborn person who you can't communicate with)

524
00:39:55,400 --> 00:39:59,250
Ah, you're talking about the dumb-head stranger, right?

525
00:39:59,250 --> 00:40:02,870
Ah, that person? Fine.

526
00:40:02,870 --> 00:40:05,140
That person previously

527
00:40:05,140 --> 00:40:09,750
raised an appeal to kick me out.

528
00:40:10,610 --> 00:40:14,420
It will be okay if we assign that person to investigate.

529
00:40:26,520 --> 00:40:30,090
- I was wrong, ajussi.
- Why did you do it?

530
00:40:31,100 --> 00:40:35,260
Why did you help that person without saying a word to me or to Lee Shin Jeok?

531
00:40:35,260 --> 00:40:36,600
I was wrong.

532
00:40:36,600 --> 00:40:39,470
He only has a temper but he doesn't think before doing something.

533
00:40:39,470 --> 00:40:42,730
For the goal in front of him, he couldn't distinguish between fire and water.

534
00:40:42,730 --> 00:40:44,730
Why did you help him?

535
00:40:45,880 --> 00:40:47,330
Didn't I ask you?

536
00:40:48,000 --> 00:40:49,930
Because we are similar.

537
00:40:50,840 --> 00:40:53,570
The people of my village

538
00:40:53,570 --> 00:40:56,060
only have quick tempers and don't think twice when doing things.

539
00:40:56,060 --> 00:40:58,220
They can't distinguish whether what's in front of them is fire or water.

540
00:40:58,220 --> 00:41:01,200
That's why the people of your village died.

541
00:41:01,200 --> 00:41:03,250
Yes, I know.

542
00:41:03,250 --> 00:41:05,200
But we...

543
00:41:06,720 --> 00:41:08,740
the people...

544
00:41:09,980 --> 00:41:14,010
are like that—because we are suffering in hope.

545
00:41:15,070 --> 00:41:17,960
We gain hope and lose it.

546
00:41:17,960 --> 00:41:21,890
We gain hope again only to lose it. Yet again, we gain hope and lose it.

547
00:41:21,890 --> 00:41:27,190
Because we keep on being like that, we get quick tempers and don't think twice.

548
00:41:27,190 --> 00:41:29,800
We don't even know how to distinguish methods.

549
00:41:31,310 --> 00:41:33,580
That's how we became like that.

550
00:41:34,340 --> 00:41:38,010
I was wrong, Ajussi. I am really sorry, but

551
00:41:40,040 --> 00:41:43,450
just like I went to Ham Joo to find you,

552
00:41:44,800 --> 00:41:47,710
to Bang Won your plan

553
00:41:48,320 --> 00:41:50,710
is probably his only hope for survival.

554
00:41:50,710 --> 00:41:52,470
You and Lee Bang Won are different.

555
00:41:52,470 --> 00:41:55,890
No. We are not different.

556
00:41:57,460 --> 00:42:01,570
I first met Lee Bang Won when I was young and went to Gaegyeong to find my mom.

557
00:42:01,570 --> 00:42:05,300
At that time, to help those of us who were in a difficult situation, that child

558
00:42:05,300 --> 00:42:07,000
was the one who led us.

559
00:42:07,000 --> 00:42:09,690
Also, that Lee Bang Won that I met again after growing up

560
00:42:09,690 --> 00:42:14,300
risked himself in order to help us, like always.

561
00:42:16,010 --> 00:42:18,760
Among the powerful people I have seen,

562
00:42:18,760 --> 00:42:21,270
they were all people who have taken things from us.

563
00:42:21,270 --> 00:42:23,160
But that person

564
00:42:23,800 --> 00:42:26,850
was the first nobleman to help us.

565
00:42:28,810 --> 00:42:31,570
Also, that person, more than anyone else...

566
00:42:31,570 --> 00:42:33,000
No. More than myself.

567
00:42:33,000 --> 00:42:36,000
He wishes for your plan to succeed.

568
00:42:36,000 --> 00:42:37,820
That's why I,

569
00:42:38,440 --> 00:42:42,400
more than anyone else, wish for Teacher Sam Bong's plan to succeed.

570
00:42:42,400 --> 00:42:46,240
To defeat the Do Dang officials, turn the tables, and proudly,

571
00:42:46,240 --> 00:42:49,100
proudly live with strength in my guts!

572
00:42:49,100 --> 00:42:51,400
I wish to live like that.

573
00:42:51,400 --> 00:42:53,330
That's why

574
00:42:53,890 --> 00:42:58,670
he waited, waited, and waited some more, in that room,

575
00:42:59,350 --> 00:43:01,780
for you to quickly come.

576
00:43:03,260 --> 00:43:06,090
Ajussi, you have to quickly come back.

577
00:43:06,090 --> 00:43:08,750
We will be waiting.

578
00:43:11,590 --> 00:43:14,340
I know that both Bang Won and I are wrong, Ajussi.

579
00:43:14,340 --> 00:43:18,410
Still, to Bang Won and I,

580
00:43:18,410 --> 00:43:21,130
please give us a chance to make up for our wrongdoings.

581
00:43:21,930 --> 00:43:24,910
Please save Bang Won, Ajussi.

582
00:43:28,590 --> 00:43:30,480
Ham Joo

583
00:43:30,480 --> 00:43:35,040
Shin-dong, Im-dong, Yang-dong.
(Lee Ji Ran)

584
00:43:35,040 --> 00:43:37,910
If we strike these three strongholds, Ho Bal Do's incoming troops
(Ho Bal Do: Yeojin tribe's Chief)

585
00:43:37,910 --> 00:43:40,920
will all be defeated by our Ga Byeol Cho.

586
00:43:41,960 --> 00:43:46,390
As I said, they will be in a situation where they cannot move or back out! If we launch a surprise attack at daybreak,

587
00:43:46,390 --> 00:43:49,060
Ho Bal Do's main force cannot organize their battle line

588
00:43:49,060 --> 00:43:51,040
and we can annihilate them.

589
00:43:51,040 --> 00:43:52,480
Lee Seong Gye

590
00:43:52,480 --> 00:43:57,050
Between five and seven o'clock in the morning,

591
00:43:57,050 --> 00:43:58,670
we will launch a full-scale attack.

592
00:43:58,670 --> 00:44:00,840
Yes, General!

593
00:44:12,650 --> 00:44:14,830
What happened to Bang Won, and why did you come alone?

594
00:44:14,830 --> 00:44:18,620
Did you send the documents to withdraw the An Byeon Book?

595
00:44:20,550 --> 00:44:22,790
Why are you not saying anything?

596
00:44:24,130 --> 00:44:27,510
I didn't send the documents.

597
00:44:27,510 --> 00:44:29,150
What are you saying right now?

598
00:44:29,150 --> 00:44:32,030
Bang Won was arrested by the investigation office.

599
00:44:34,480 --> 00:44:35,610
For what?

600
00:44:35,610 --> 00:44:38,690
As a condition for approving the An Byeon Book, Hong In Bang and Father

601
00:44:38,690 --> 00:44:43,390
will divide the Northeastern region tax revenue between yourselves. He was charged for illegally negotiating that.

602
00:44:44,890 --> 00:44:50,100
Lee In Gyeom has proclaimed war against our family.

603
00:44:50,100 --> 00:44:53,900
So, as the eldest son of the Jeon Joo Lee Family,

604
00:44:53,900 --> 00:44:57,120
I decided in your stead.

605
00:44:58,230 --> 00:45:04,160
We have never avoided a fight when our family's name was on the line, Father.

606
00:45:06,000 --> 00:45:09,050
Shouldn't we save Bang Won?

607
00:45:09,050 --> 00:45:12,060
If Bang Won has to die for what he did wrong,

608
00:45:12,060 --> 00:45:14,330
it has to be by our hands,

609
00:45:14,330 --> 00:45:16,540
not Lee In Gyeom's.

610
00:45:17,920 --> 00:45:20,610
In a situation where we have an upcoming huge battle,

611
00:45:20,610 --> 00:45:23,640
I am sorry for saying this.

612
00:45:24,720 --> 00:45:26,380
No.

613
00:45:27,390 --> 00:45:30,440
We have another reason to win.

614
00:45:34,850 --> 00:45:37,670
Let's take Ho Bal Do's head

615
00:45:37,670 --> 00:45:40,150
and discuss the next case.

616
00:45:41,100 --> 00:45:45,540
Daronggarongjoorong... Daronggarongjoorong...

617
00:45:50,780 --> 00:45:52,980
This really doesn't get loose.

618
00:45:56,570 --> 00:45:58,700
That's right!
(Jukryong: Bi Guk Temple's Head Monk)

619
00:45:58,700 --> 00:46:02,530
Who am I? I am Bi Guk Temple's Jukryong!

620
00:46:11,990 --> 00:46:14,680
How could you treat a person like this?

621
00:46:15,670 --> 00:46:19,070
The situation outside has become urgent so we have been busy.

622
00:46:19,070 --> 00:46:21,430
I will explain our stand while we go.

623
00:46:21,430 --> 00:46:23,000
Go?

624
00:46:25,160 --> 00:46:27,290
Where are we going?

625
00:46:27,290 --> 00:46:29,390
You have to go to Gaegyeong with me.

626
00:46:29,390 --> 00:46:33,670
I will relay to Head of Seonggyungwan Hong In Bang the Ga Byeol Cho's stance.

627
00:46:35,720 --> 00:46:37,960
- You're going to release me?
- Yes.

628
00:46:37,960 --> 00:46:40,090
- Right now?
- Yes.

629
00:46:41,460 --> 00:46:45,510
Damn it. They should've released me earlier.

630
00:46:49,840 --> 00:46:52,090
If something bad happens to Lee Bang Won,

631
00:46:52,090 --> 00:46:54,490
you said we would gain four things from that.

632
00:46:55,310 --> 00:46:58,080
What's the last one?

633
00:46:58,610 --> 00:47:00,740
I

634
00:47:02,700 --> 00:47:07,030
find your hesitation a pity, Bon Won.

635
00:47:08,940 --> 00:47:11,790
I became like that the more I understood.

636
00:47:14,220 --> 00:47:16,680
"Am I right?"

637
00:47:17,790 --> 00:47:19,600
"Am I also

638
00:47:20,860 --> 00:47:24,240
becoming like other politicians?"

639
00:47:26,510 --> 00:47:29,300
It's because I was scared like that.

640
00:47:32,240 --> 00:47:34,360
By it,

641
00:47:34,360 --> 00:47:37,470
at the moment of the great cause's desperation,

642
00:47:39,540 --> 00:47:42,460
I feared that I am wrong like this.

643
00:47:45,620 --> 00:47:48,070
You are right, Bon Won.

644
00:47:48,070 --> 00:47:50,480
Don't be scared.

645
00:47:50,480 --> 00:47:52,200
Yes,

646
00:47:53,020 --> 00:47:55,080
I am scared.

647
00:47:55,810 --> 00:47:58,710
But I

648
00:47:59,860 --> 00:48:04,130
am me because I am always scared.

649
00:48:05,050 --> 00:48:06,820
So,

650
00:48:08,680 --> 00:48:12,960
I will not use your scheme.

651
00:48:15,440 --> 00:48:18,100
Watch Lee In Gyeom's movements.

652
00:48:18,950 --> 00:48:21,640
What kind of movement are you talking about?

653
00:48:21,640 --> 00:48:25,880
It will be hard to accuse Lee Seong Gye just on a letter and some rumors.

654
00:48:25,880 --> 00:48:29,690
He will fabricate some sort of evidence next.

655
00:48:29,690 --> 00:48:31,920
Watch him while keeping that in mind.

656
00:48:31,920 --> 00:48:33,980
That's right.

657
00:48:33,980 --> 00:48:38,130
This is totally Hong In Bang's handwriting!

658
00:48:38,130 --> 00:48:39,530
Yes.

659
00:48:39,530 --> 00:48:43,900
Since three years ago, I have been training one of my staff to imitate writing.

660
00:48:43,900 --> 00:48:46,730
Great, great.

661
00:48:47,330 --> 00:48:49,540
Now, this...

662
00:48:49,540 --> 00:48:52,450
You can just put it in Lee Bang Won's residence.

663
00:48:53,480 --> 00:48:55,270
Tomorrow, the investigation office

664
00:48:56,460 --> 00:48:58,780
will conduct a search there.

665
00:48:58,780 --> 00:49:00,530
Yes.

666
00:49:00,530 --> 00:49:05,480
Since, the secret agreement is written in detail, it will become confirmed evidence.

667
00:49:05,480 --> 00:49:10,670
Now, Lee Seong Gye's moral integrity will collapse.

668
00:49:10,670 --> 00:49:14,210
With that, to prove his innocence,

669
00:49:14,210 --> 00:49:19,580
he will have no choice but to withdraw the An Byeon Book.

670
00:49:20,620 --> 00:49:24,200
His alliance with Hong In Bang will also be broken.

671
00:49:24,200 --> 00:49:26,000
I will be going.

672
00:50:06,420 --> 00:50:08,830
I have placed it there according to your orders.

673
00:50:09,540 --> 00:50:10,940
Let's go.

674
00:50:30,510 --> 00:50:32,950
Now, Lee In Gyeom's desire is confirmed.
(Through An Byeon Book, the tax revenue of Northeastern region to be split between Hong In Bang, Gil Tae Mi and Lee Seong Gye.)

675
00:50:32,950 --> 00:50:37,100
After fabricating evidence like this, General Lee Seong Gye's reputation will fall to the ground
(Through Go Gong Chong Rang Gil Yoo being appointed as Northeastern region tax inspector, Lee Seong Gye and Gil Tae Mi's connection is confirmed.)

676
00:50:37,100 --> 00:50:40,340
while Hong In Bang and Gil Tae Mi will be driven into a corner.

677
00:50:40,340 --> 00:50:42,100
Fortunately, I was able to remove it today.

678
00:50:42,100 --> 00:50:45,180
But what are we going to do in the future?

679
00:50:49,170 --> 00:50:53,040
Change the letter to this and put it in that place.

680
00:50:58,200 --> 00:51:02,560
I will turn the tables with this.

681
00:51:04,750 --> 00:51:07,270
Everyone scatter and search thoroughly!

682
00:51:07,270 --> 00:51:08,930
Yes!

683
00:51:16,550 --> 00:51:17,650
Search thoroughly!

684
00:51:17,650 --> 00:51:19,670
Yes!

685
00:51:26,190 --> 00:51:28,660
- Search!
- Yes!

686
00:51:38,370 --> 00:51:41,760
Sir, we found something strange.

687
00:51:53,130 --> 00:51:56,860
They say that Lee Seong Gye's residence in Gaegyeong has been searched.

688
00:51:56,860 --> 00:51:59,490
Finally, he's making this issue bigger?

689
00:51:59,490 --> 00:52:03,340
They said that the dumb head in charge of the investigation is upright

690
00:52:03,340 --> 00:52:04,910
so we can believe in him.

691
00:52:04,910 --> 00:52:07,940
Using whatever method he can, Hap Ha

692
00:52:07,940 --> 00:52:11,620
will stop the An Byeon Book and break off our alliance.

693
00:52:11,620 --> 00:52:15,220
Whatever comes out of the investigation today is only to push us out.

694
00:52:15,220 --> 00:52:16,390
What can we do now?

695
00:52:16,390 --> 00:52:18,920
There will be something.

696
00:52:18,920 --> 00:52:20,680
Something...

697
00:52:22,010 --> 00:52:25,760
But at this crucial moment, where is Sam Bong?

698
00:52:25,760 --> 00:52:28,640
He said he will be going to Ham Joo...

699
00:52:51,290 --> 00:52:53,400
Today,

700
00:52:53,400 --> 00:52:57,980
regarding the investigation of related materials to the An Byeon Book,

701
00:52:57,980 --> 00:53:00,600
with the many members of the Do Dang,

702
00:53:00,600 --> 00:53:03,890
I want to have a consultation.

703
00:53:04,610 --> 00:53:06,510
Today, at the investigation office,

704
00:53:06,510 --> 00:53:11,340
we heard that there was a search conducted at General Lee Seong Gye's residence.

705
00:53:11,340 --> 00:53:13,330
Have you received the report?

706
00:53:13,330 --> 00:53:15,050
No.

707
00:53:15,740 --> 00:53:19,600
He will come to the Do Dang himself and report.

708
00:53:21,820 --> 00:53:25,900
That way, there will be no unnecessary misunderstanding.

709
00:53:25,900 --> 00:53:28,090
Open it!

710
00:53:50,900 --> 00:53:54,470
I am an officer of the investigation office.

711
00:53:54,470 --> 00:53:59,650
So that there will be no doubts regarding this investigation,

712
00:53:59,650 --> 00:54:02,180
to personally inform you about it

713
00:54:02,180 --> 00:54:04,020
I came to this place.

714
00:54:04,020 --> 00:54:06,490
Have you found anything worthy of being evidence?

715
00:54:06,490 --> 00:54:11,290
Today, from the hours of Jin to Mi, we conducted a search.
(hours of Jin: 7-9 AM, hours of Mi: 1-3 PM)

716
00:54:11,290 --> 00:54:13,540
This was found.

717
00:54:17,990 --> 00:54:24,160
Then, read the contents of that letter to everyone.

718
00:54:24,160 --> 00:54:25,670
Yes.

719
00:54:27,010 --> 00:54:31,760
This was found in Lee Bang Won's room.

720
00:54:38,320 --> 00:54:42,170
No matter how long I wait, you don't appear.

721
00:54:42,170 --> 00:54:44,710
According to your plan,

722
00:54:47,860 --> 00:54:50,590
I killed Baek Yoon first.

723
00:54:50,590 --> 00:54:53,180
Who is the next person?

724
00:54:59,940 --> 00:55:01,810
What?

725
00:55:04,040 --> 00:55:06,860
Weren't you going to save Lee Bang Won?

726
00:55:06,860 --> 00:55:08,510
But mentioning Baek Yoon's murder?

727
00:55:08,510 --> 00:55:12,830
Why did you place the letter the Viper left behind in Lee Bang Won's residence?

728
00:55:12,830 --> 00:55:14,860
Don't you get it?

729
00:55:14,860 --> 00:55:19,120
I don't. This is a different matter than the illegal dealings regarding the An Byeon Book.

730
00:55:19,120 --> 00:55:22,210
Lee Bang Won can die with just this accusation.

731
00:55:22,210 --> 00:55:25,190
Really? Will he die?

732
00:55:25,190 --> 00:55:27,090
Bon Won!

733
00:55:28,650 --> 00:55:32,670
An intelligent snake will not swallow a boar.

734
00:55:32,670 --> 00:55:33,740
Yes?

735
00:55:33,740 --> 00:55:37,320
If it does, it will break its jaw and its stomach will explode.

736
00:55:37,320 --> 00:55:42,790
Lee In Gyeom is an intelligent and sensible snake.

737
00:55:43,600 --> 00:55:47,750
Also, the current Do Dang can't handle a problem of this level.

738
00:55:47,750 --> 00:55:50,520
What exactly are you talking about?

739
00:55:50,520 --> 00:55:52,630
All of this

740
00:55:52,630 --> 00:55:56,980
is possible because Lee Bang Won is Lee Seong Gye's son.

741
00:56:01,050 --> 00:56:03,960
The letter got changed.

742
00:56:03,960 --> 00:56:09,560
The Elder is crazy. Even if he's just manipulating, how can he put in something that enormous?

743
00:56:09,560 --> 00:56:13,640
He's going to corner Lee Seong Gye as Baek Yoon's killer?

744
00:56:14,430 --> 00:56:16,520
This was forged. It's impossible.

745
00:56:16,520 --> 00:56:19,830
What reason would Lee Seong Gye have to kill Baek Yoon?

746
00:56:19,830 --> 00:56:23,920
The one who ordered Baek Yoon to be killed was Lee Seong Gye?

747
00:56:23,920 --> 00:56:26,740
Is he saying that he will go into war with Lee Seong Gye?

748
00:56:26,740 --> 00:56:29,240
